Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.55,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"11 Years Ago, The Day Reia Died・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,"Dear Kureha, I'm going to send her back\Nthrough the door. Don't worry, okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's "her"? What's the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You found Kureha that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let Kureha's precious friend be excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Someday, the time will come when\Nbears and people can be friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:07.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this pendant with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a love charm. I know it will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:48.67,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to become\Ntrue friends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,"THE DOOR TO FRIENDSHIP"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:47.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:47.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Rowr?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I came {\i1}way {\i0}close to taking you\Nfor a bear and shooting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do things that'll confuse people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... I thought I was way busted...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:05.68,Main,,0,0,0,,N-N-No, growl! U-Um... what's that truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A special vehicle developed\Njust for bear annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.39,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Bear-Killing Beam Truck・(Weapon of Destruction)"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Buzz buzz! Nasty nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,We cyborgized the dead bear,\Nand we're using her to generate electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Fight fire with fire! And bears with bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Eco-kumagical! Nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,So, have you seen any bears in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:54.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We have reports of another bear\Nsighting near the school this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I know nothing, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Really! I haven't seen one single bear, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears will get you, too,\Nif you hang out here all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You should watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:18.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if it's not here either,\Nwhere should I look next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it. Why did\NLulu Yurigasaki betray Ginko Yurishiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she wished for Ginko\NYurishiro's love to be returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Her actions are inconsistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:40.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so dense. It's because\NLulu Yurigasaki loves Ginko Yurishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Love comes in many forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's why Kumaria questions\Neveryone who tries to go beyond severance:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,"Is your love the real thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Then she laid down a ladder for the girls,\Nconnecting the two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,A single, vast mirror stood\Nlike a wall in their path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Each girl saw her own reflection in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,--They heard Kumaria's voice say,\N--Everyone, our friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:16.69,Main,,0,0,0,,--"Now, your friend is waiting on the other side of that door.\N--Everyone, our friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--"Now, your friend is waiting on the other side of that door.\N--is now being put to the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,--"Now, your friend is waiting on the other side of that door.\N--The Wall of Severance has broken down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,--If you smash the 'you' in the mirror to bits,\N--thanks to evil's way unfair betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--I if you tear it apart,\N--There's nothing protecting us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--she shall grant you a Promise Kiss.\N--Which is exactly why we must fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:30.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--she shall grant you a Promise Kiss.\N--Let's exclude the bear lurking among us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.08,Main,,0,0,0,,--But beware: this may cost you your life.\N--Let's exclude the bear lurking among us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,--But beware: this may cost you your life.\N--with our own hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,--But beware: this may cost you your life.\N--and take back our invisible lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,--I will ask you one more time: Is your love the real thing?"\N--and take back our invisible lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The girls stared at themselves in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the rest of the book...\NThe future Mom wanted to tell me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Moon Girl and the Forest Girl"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,The moon girl summoned up all her courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"I want to cross the sky.\NSo I will smash myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,The forest girl steeled herself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,"I want to cross the sky.\NSo I will tear myself apart."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,"My love is true!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:27.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The mirror shattered in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,And they each found their friend\Nstanding on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,The two girls walked slowly up to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:41.35,Main,,0,0,0,,and simply, wordlessly gave\Neach other their Promise Kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, having completed their Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,the two began a journey beyond\Nseverance, guided by the star of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:59.75,Main,,0,0,0,,This is our destiny? Our rightful future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She and I... Ginko and I\Nwill go beyond severance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear and a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That future just isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,A prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That's Mom's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I came to give it back, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... want a bath before you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom used to wash my hair\Nlike this, way back when.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:10:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It was Miss Yuriika who killed my mother.\NShe was a bear, like you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,May I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that Mitsuko Yurizono\Nwas the one who killed Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,So why did Ginko tell me {\i1}she {\i0}did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what Ginko thinks, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,She knew that Mitsuko was after Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:34.76,Main,,0,0,0,,But she didn't save her. She couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,She loves you, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0},\Nso she wanted your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,But with Sumika around,\Nshe wouldn't be able to get that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko was jealous of Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm no better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I was jealous of you.\NThat's why I said those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko was Sumika's killer's accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt like you'd stolen Ginko's love from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,after I wished all this time for\Nyou two to do your Promise Kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:20.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,So this really was the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,See, that proves you were friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:44.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko won't lie to you. She can't, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Because you're her precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Precious friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,--Growl...\N--Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you remember something, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no good. I still can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom told me. Ginko was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl I loved, who sang the love song\Nwith me when I was little, was Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet I forgot her.\NI can't even remember her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? Why are my only missing\Nmemories the ones of Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:42.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko loves you anyway, you know.\NThen and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko doesn't back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}, will you forgive her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... Will you please be her friend again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you please love her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I... can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Humans and bears...\Nwe have severance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,No one can overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...\NLost love never comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,"Incoming Call: Blocked Number"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki, you're in trouble!\NYou have a bear targeting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro and Lulu Yurigasaki\Nare really bears in disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,We just found evidence. One of them\Nmust be the bear you missed on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:51.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Which means you're way in danger!\NShe's bound to come for her revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Call us the second you\Nsense a bear nearby, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,She must've caught on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But we won't let her escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... Why are you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But I'm sure\Nit's the right thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Search every corner of the neighborhood.\NIt's time for our final sprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}... I think I might know\Nthe reason you lost your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,For a bear to become a girl,\Nshe has to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A deal? With whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:23.17,Main,,0,0,0,,With what stands between humans\Nand bears--the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The Wall... You mean the men on the phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If they grant a bear yuri\Napproval in court, she can become a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But to do that, you have to let go\Nof whatever you care about most.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,This is just my theory, but I bet in\NGinko's trial, she let go of your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.53,Main,,0,0,0,,My love...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:56.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, the love you gave\Nher all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:16:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why Ginko disappeared from your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:05.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Muahaha! I'm so clever--right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure you can get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Get what back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Your love for Ginko.\NBecause you didn't really give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe. And now this\Nreally is goodbye, huh, Kure{\i1}-chin{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:33.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu Yurigasaki has revealed the secret\Nof transformation to a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Her yuri approval is terminated,\Neffective immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw! Can't we do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we cannot. Rules are cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:17:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}. I told you the truth,\Nso I can't be a girl anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.40,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't be together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:41.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty, nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a way different bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure... {\i1}chin{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let a friend be excluded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:28.07,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"The Day They Met・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's that? Who's calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:43.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"There is one way to make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,In the center of the sky, there is\Na place called the Door to Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:19:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,If your love is true,\Nyour friend will be waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...on the other side."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:28.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the "Door to Friendship"\Nthat was in the picture book!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I met Ginko on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It is! I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.68,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Who's calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, you're not alone. I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is where it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I crossed the Wall of Severance\Nthat day and met Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko, you're my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You can get to the other side\Nof the wall through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.55,Main,,0,0,0,,You can go safely back to the bear world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl... Did I manage to become your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:12.65,Main,,0,0,0,,No. You are not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, I won't forgive bears.\NThe next time I see you, I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I know I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Go. Get out of here, now. Never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to this stupid world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,This was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew the evil was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:15.04,Main,,0,0,0,,"Evil = Kureha Tsubaki"\NThe lily opens!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I way saw what you did. Who knew this\Nwas a secret passage through severance?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:25.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who brought\Nbears into our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You joined the bears, and you've been\Ntaking revenge on us for excluding you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki, you're going to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,for taking our friends' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, the hunt's just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:48.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat her, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:17.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:51.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.73,0:24:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:29.47,Main,,0,0,0,,We now begin the Yuri Trial.
